Paper: hep-th/9703186

Date: 1997-03-26

Title: Simple Derivation of the Picard-Fuchs equations for the Seiberg-Witten

ModelsComments: LaTex file, 10 pages. some missprints are corrected

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B418 (1998) 317-323

A closed form of the Picard-Fuchs equations for N=2 supersymmetricYang-Mills theories with massless hypermultiplet are obtained for classical Liegauge groups. We consider any number of massless matter in fundamentalrepresentation so as to keep the theory asymptotically free.